abusefilter-revert-title: Malum lebese teere woo n tee filita la puan $1
abusefilter-revert-intro:
Wãna wa basɛ ti fu malum tãna lebesa la teere duma la woo n tee dɔla 'abuse' filita puan sɛla n sɔi la de la filita $1.
N beleni mɛ nyɔkɛ fu mɛŋɛ lɔgetuna tuuma puan.
abusefilter-revert-preview-item:
$1: $2 {{GENDER:$7|masem}} a $3 on $4. 
Itegɔ n yeti di malum lebese: $5 ($6)
abusefilter-revert-search-legend: Loe 'abuse' filita itegɔ ti la malum lebe pooren
abusefilter-revert-preview-no-results: Query la ka nyɛ iteseko n nari ti a malum lebese bu.
abusefilter-revert-preview-intro:
Sɛla n boi tilum wa de la itegɔ duma ti 'abuse' dikɛ ti ba malum lebese itegɔ duma la n iŋɛ la. 
N beleni mɛ kɛkɛ ba suŋa, de di'e "{{int:abusefilter-revert-confirm}}" ti fu nam fum n loe sɛla la.
abusefilter-revert-success: Fu malum dikɛ itegɔ la wuusa ti 'abuse' filita iŋɛ la lebe la pooren se'ere zuo n sɔi la [[Special: AbuseFilter/$1|filter $2]].
abusefilter-revert-reason:
Itegɔ duma la ti 'abuse' filita iŋɛ la mɛŋɛ n malum lebe pooren se'ere zuo n sɔi la filita $1.
Se'ere zuo n sɔi la: $2
abusefilter-test: Dikɛ filita la tɛɛsum la demesego duma sɛba n tole la
abusefilter-test-intro:
Pɛgerɛ wa basɛ mɛ ti fu tãna kɛkɛra filita n kɛ daka n boi tilum 'against the Last' $1 {{PLURAL:$1 change|changes}}.
Fu San yeti fu yuregɛ faali sɛka n pugum bɔna, gulesɛ ka filita ID kɛ'ɛsɛ daka la puan tilum demesego 'texbox' puan de di'e "{{int:abusefilter-test-load}}" tilum.
abusefilter-test-page: Teere duma n tee pɛgerɛ puan:
abusefilter-test-shownegative: Pa'alɛ teere duma n tee ka tɔ filita la
abusefilter-test-syntaxerr: Filita la ti fu kɛ'ɛsɛ la tari la 'syntax error'. Fu ta'am nyɛ gãresegɔ mɔɔnɛ fu san di'e "{{int:abusefilter-edit-check}}" button.
abusefilter-examine-intro: Pɛgerɛ wa basɛ mɛ ti fu gɛɛla sɛla woo n boi lɛŋa lɛŋa 'generated by the Abuse' filita bɔ'ɔra nɛra woo teere, de tɛɛsena ka fɔbera filita duma.
abusefilter-examine-intro-examine-only: Pɛgerɛ wa basɛ mɛ ti fu gɛɛla sɛla woo n boi lɛŋa lɛŋa 'generated by the Abuse' filita bɔ'ɔra nɛra woo teere.
abusefilter-examine-match: Filita la tɔ teere la mɛ
abusefilter-examine-nomatch: Filita la ka tɔ la teere la.
abusefilter-examine-notfound: Teere la ti fu ɛɛra la ka boi.
abusefilter-examine-incompatible: Teere la ti fu ɛɛra la Abuse filita ka suŋɛ ka
abusefilter-examine-noresults: Ruzɔɔsi ka boi eere zɔ la ti fu dikɛ bɔ' la puan.
abusefilter-log-header:
Log wa pa'ali la teere  kilesego n tee filita duma la puan.
San dɛna gãresegɔ mɔɔnɛ, bisɛ [[Special: AbuseFilter/history|the list]] n de nananawa filita teere duma.
abusefilter-log-invalid-filter: 'Specified' filita ID duma la basɛba de la 'invalid'.
abusefilter-import-intro:
Fu ta'am dikɛ 'interface' wa tum ta tari filita la yakɛ na ze'ele wiki ayima puan na. Wiki la n ze'ele zi'an na la, di'e "{{int:abusefilter-edit-export}}" bɔna "{{int:abusefilter-edit-tools}}" n boi demesego 'interface' la puan.
Tɔgesɛ ze'ele 'textbox' la yese na la puan, de dikɛ ka kɛ'ɛsɛ 'textbox' wa puan, dee di'e "{{int:abusefilter-import-dubmit}}".
abusefilter-import-invalid-data: Data la ti fu tiregera ti fu dikɛ yakɛ na la ka de 'valid'
abusefilter-view-privatedetails-reason: Sɛla zuo ti fu 'accesing private' gãresegɔ:
abusefilter-invalid-request: 'Invalid request!' see ti fu 'access private log' gãresegɔ dɔla la 'form' n boi [[Special:AbuseLog/$1]] de bɔ se'ere zuo n sɔi la.
abusefilter-invalid-request-noid: 'Invalid request!' see ti fu 'access private log'gãresegɔ dɔla la 'form'n boi 'abuse log' gãresegɔ pɛgerɛ de bɔ se'ere zuo n sɔi la.
abusefilter-blocked-domains-intro: 'External' linki duma n tɔɔri yu'ura wa na gu ba san dikɛ pa'asera pɛgerɛ wa puan. 'Domains ana wa 'stored' bɔna la [[MediaWiki:BlockedExternalDomains.json]].
abusefilter-blocked-domains-add-explanat: Kalam, fu ta'am dikɛ 'domain' pa'asɛ 'domain' sɛba yu'ura nngu la puan.
abusefilter-blocked-domains-domain: 'Domain' n yeti a gu, wuu wikipedia.org
abusefilter-blocked-domains-remove-expla: Pɛgerɛ wa puan fu ta'am yese 'domain' n gu basɛ
